      "html": "<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2 flex items-center\">💎 太晶化材料獲取方式</h3>\n<p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6 border-l-4 border-gray-200 pl-3\">\n    本攻略資料來自玩家社群分享，本站進行整理與修改。<br>\n    原作者：♚伊比利小豬♚ ／\n    <a href=\"https://discord.com/channels/1088052757350596608/1447965630639771738\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-600\">來源連結</a><br>\n    若原作者不希望本站收錄，請聯絡我們，將立即移除。\n</p>\n<div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\n\n    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 border rounded p-4\">\n        <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2\">1️⃣ 太晶碎片</p>\n        <p class=\"text-sm\">與野生寶可夢對戰，有機率掉落各屬性太晶碎片</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"bg-gray-50 border rounded p-4\">\n        <p class=\"font-bold text-blue-800 mb-2\">2️⃣ 太晶球材料</p>\n        <ul class=\"list-disc ml-5 space-y-1 text-sm\">\n            <li><strong>終界珍珠：</strong>終界 安德、未知圖騰掉落物</li>\n            <li><strong>烈焰粉：</strong>地獄 烈焰使者生怪磚</li>\n            <li><strong>羊毛：</strong>綿羊寶可夢</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">感謝 Life_0901 玩家補充</p>\n    </div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-4 p-4 bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 text-gray-800\">💡 <b>小提醒：</b>每次太晶化需要消耗 <strong>50 個太晶碎片</strong>。</div>"
